# Hyperfluent-arch GRUB Theme Information
# =======================================

## Theme Name: hyperfluent-arch
## Description: Modern, sleek GRUB theme with Arch Linux styling
## Compatible with: GRUB 2.x, LUKS encryption

## Download Sources (try in order):
# Primary source
https://github.com/rhythmcreative/hyperfluent-grub-theme/archive/refs/heads/main.tar.gz

# Alternative sources
https://github.com/saber-linux/hyperfluent-grub-theme/archive/refs/heads/main.tar.gz
https://github.com/prasanthrangan/hyprdots/raw/main/Source/arcs/Grub_themes/hyperfluent-arch.tar.gz
https://github.com/ChrisTitusTech/hyprland-titus/raw/main/grub-themes/hyperfluent-arch.tar.gz

## Manual Installation:
# If automatic download fails, you can:
# 1. Download hyperfluent-arch.tar.gz manually from any working source
# 2. Place it in ~/.cache/grub-theme/
# 3. Run the installer script again

## Features:
# - Modern UI design
# - High resolution support (1920x1080, 1366x768, 1024x768)
# - LUKS encryption support
# - Automatic GRUB configuration
# - Easy uninstall option

## Usage:
# Install: ./Scripts/install_grub_theme.sh install
# Remove:  ./Scripts/install_grub_theme.sh uninstall
# Help:    ./Scripts/install_grub_theme.sh --help

